body:
Comment 2: 
It looks like NetBSD 6.0 beta 2 was released in May 2012.
The real NetBSD 6.0 was released in October 2012.
The next version, NetBSD 6.1, was released in May 2013.
NetBSD 6.1.3 was just released in January 2014.
Have you tried any of those newer versions?

NetBSD is not one of the supported systems, so if someone wants to fix this for Go 1.3
that's fine, but I don't believe we are going to spend effort on it ourselves.
